{"tid":2413604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩岸 20210219 星期五 蘋果日報","createTime":"2021-02-18T23:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T06:37:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c5a69283e34ecf7756678a3c25961d8c8523a8","tid":2413604,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T23:55:09.000Z","msg":"兩岸 20210219 星期五 蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/daily/china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fdaily%2Fchina%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69HhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=608be601\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fdaily%2Fchina%2F&h=88c76599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/daily/china/</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報慈善基金<br />\n<br />\n茅台集團女質量官 獲薦工程院士惹爭議 <br />\n官媒也質疑 斥「市場因素」影響<br />\n<br />\n中共新星郭寧寧膺《時代》百大次世代<br />\n<br />\n反美教授自爆居德州被嘲<br />\n<br />\n美撿千萬華製假N95 <br />\n冒3M進口 流入12州<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮詩人「被中國籍」韓教授促糾正<br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n5小時前<br />\n茅台集團女質量官 獲薦工程院士惹爭議 官媒也質疑 斥「市場因素」影響<br />\n<br />\n■茅台酒紙箱也被炒起。<br />\n5小時前<br />\n散裝扮原盒 茅台紙箱炒至六百元<br />\n<br />\n■中國工程院是中國工程技術界最高榮譽性、諮詢性學術機構。<br />\n5小時前<br />\n最高學術稱號須過兩關<br />\n<br />\n5小時前<br />\n中共新星郭寧寧膺《時代》百大次世代<br />\n<br />\n■「反美教授」陳平長居美國惹網民狂轟。<br />\n5小時前<br />\n反美教授自爆居德州被嘲<br />\n<br />\n5小時前<br />\n美撿千萬華製假N95 冒3M進口 流入12州<br />\n<br />\nBioNTech疫苗<br />\n5小時前<br />\nBioNTech承諾按計劃售台疫苗<br />\n<br />\n5小時前<br />\n朝鮮詩人「被中國籍」韓教授促糾正<br />\n<br />\n數碼人民幣<br />\n5小時前<br />\n京深試行數碼人幣 恐增監控隱憂<br />\n<br />\n5小時前<br />\n涉槍殺七人潛逃 黑龍江男證身亡<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n最Hit<br />\n<br />\n杜鵑預計移動路線圖。天文台圖片<br />\n5小時前<br />\n熱帶風暴｜ 牛年第一風暴杜鵑 料增強逼近香港警戒線<br />\n<br />\n5小時前<br />\n老店收爐 - 左丁山"},{"pid":"2f9d662590062c97890dc7931b0bed72cf7f02b4","tid":2413604,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T01:32:38.000Z","msg":"反美教授自爆居德州被嘲<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210219/M5HXG4SOBNHT7B477KYC6FQJSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210219%2FM5HXG4SOBNHT7B477KYC6FQJSU%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69HhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=e423c4e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210219%2FM5HXG4SOBNHT7B477KYC6FQJSU%2F&h=6b50102b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210219/M5HXG4SOBNHT7B477KYC6FQJSU/</a>"},{"pid":"ccb50fd5a8be0c6ab60fbafff000b4da7a561b31","tid":2413604,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T06:37:34.000Z","msg":"最高學術稱號須過兩關<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210219/LG6QLRUJQJFNVA5OWCQRNY3YX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210219%2FLG6QLRUJQJFNVA5OWCQRNY3YX4%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69HhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=94de38c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210219%2FLG6QLRUJQJFNVA5OWCQRNY3YX4%2F&h=55d74c85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210219/LG6QLRUJQJFNVA5OWCQRNY3YX4/</a><br />\n<br />\n■中國工程院是中國工程技術界最高榮譽性、諮詢性學術機構。<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】中國工程院院士是中國工程科學技術方面的最高學術稱號，1994年正式設立，與1955年設立的中國科學院院士並稱「兩院」院士。科學院院士面向學術型人才，工程院院士則面向技術型人才，兩者均為終身名譽，一般每兩年增選一次，每次總名額不超過60人。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。"}]}